{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "creche-latence-traces",
  "title": "Creche Planner — Latence & Traces",
  "description": "Exploration des traces distribuées via Tempo. Permet d'analyser la latence end-to-end et par service (api-gateway, svc-referentiel, svc-foyer, svc-planification, svc-tarification).",
  "tags": ["creche-planner", "traces", "latence"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 2,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      },
      {
        "datasource": {
          "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource",
          "uid": "infinity-github-deploys"
        },
        "enable": true,
        "iconColor": "purple",
        "name": "Déploiements (prod)",
        "target": {
          "refId": "Deploiements",
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "format": "table",
          "parser": "backend",
          "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/EdouardZemb/creche-planner/deployments?environment=production&per_page=30",
          "url_options": { "method": "GET" },
          "root_selector": "",
          "columns": [
            { "selector": "created_at", "text": "time", "type": "timestamp" },
            { "selector": "description", "text": "text", "type": "string" },
            { "selector": "environment", "text": "tags", "type": "string" }
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Comment utiliser ce dashboard",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Traces distribuées & métriques RED — Creche Planner\n\nCe dashboard s'appuie sur **Tempo** (backend de traces) alimenté via le collecteur OTel.\n\n- Utilisez les panneaux **Explorateur de traces** pour explorer les spans par `service.name`.\n- Filtrez par `http.route`, `http.status_code`, ou `error=true` pour isoler les erreurs.\n- Les `trace_id` apparaissent dans les logs pino des services (champ `trace_id`) — corrélation logs ↔ traces possible.\n- **Source des traces** : spans OTLP envoyés par les services NestJS → collecteur → Tempo.\n\n> **Métriques RED (Phase 13a).** Les panneaux **Débit / Erreurs / Latence p50-p95-p99** sont dérivés des traces par le **metrics generator** de Tempo (processeur `span-metrics`), poussés vers Prometheus en `remote_write` puis interrogés via la métrique `traces_spanmetrics_*`. Les percentiles ne couvrent que les spans **serveur** (`span_kind=SPAN_KIND_SERVER`, requêtes entrantes). Sans trafic récent, les séries sont vides — générez quelques requêtes pour les voir apparaître."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "traces",
      "title": "Explorateur de traces — api-gateway",
      "description": "Traces entrantes sur l'api-gateway. Filtrer par http.status_code >= 500 pour isoler les erreurs.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 12, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "${DS_TEMPO}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "query": "{ resource.service.name = \"api-gateway\" }",
          "limit": 20,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {}
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "traces",
      "title": "Explorateur de traces — svc-tarification (consumers JetStream)",
      "description": "Traces du service tarification, incluant les spans des consumers JetStream (FOYER, REFERENTIEL, PLANIFICATION).",
      "gridPos": { "h": 12, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "${DS_TEMPO}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "query": "{ resource.service.name = \"svc-tarification\" }",
          "limit": 20,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {}
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "traces",
      "title": "Explorateur de traces — erreurs toutes opérations",
      "description": "Toutes les spans marquées error=true, tous services confondus. Point d'entrée pour le triage des incidents.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 12, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 28 },
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "${DS_TEMPO}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "query": "{ status = error }",
          "limit": 20,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {}
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Métriques RED (dérivées des traces — Tempo span-metrics)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 40 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Débit de requêtes par service (req/s)",
      "description": "Rate — taux de requêtes ENTRANTES par service (spans serveur), dérivé de traces_spanmetrics_calls_total.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 41 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"]
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum by (service) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Taux d'erreurs par service (%)",
      "description": "Errors — proportion de spans serveur en erreur (status_code=STATUS_CODE_ERROR) par service. clamp_min évite la division par zéro hors trafic.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 41 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.01 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.05 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"]
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum by (service) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\", status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\"}[$__rate_interval])) / clamp_min(sum by (service) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[$__rate_interval])), 0.001)",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Latence p95 par service",
      "description": "Duration — 95e percentile de la durée des spans serveur par service, via histogram_quantile sur traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket (secondes).",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 49 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"]
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (service, le) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Latence p50 / p95 / p99 — api-gateway",
      "description": "Distribution de la latence de l'api-gateway (point d'entrée), trois percentiles dérivés de traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket (secondes).",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 49 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"]
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{service=\"api-gateway\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p50"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{service=\"api-gateway\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95"
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{service=\"api-gateway\", span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p99"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "DS_TEMPO",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "tempo",
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "label": "Tempo"
      },
      {
        "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "label": "Prometheus"
      }
    ]
  }
}
